How browser understand Javascript
Earlier days Browser has a javscript engine/javascript runtime

Google Chrome - V8
Firefox - SpiderMonkey
Old Edge - Chakra
New Edge - V8
Opera - V8

NodeJS - Javascript Run time - we can execute javascript without the help of browser
 Google Chrome - V8  - Seperate - Node Js
 We can run javascript without browser by using Node js

NPM - Node Package Manager
It come with Node js

